                                    "handle": "text_block",
                                    "label": "Band 1 — Hero (headline + body)",
                                    "config": {
                                        "content": "<h1><strong style=\"background-color: transparent;\">My name is Al.</strong></h1><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">I am a developer. I have been building websites and web applications for 30 years, working with CMS's and CRM's that whole time. I built this product because the tools that exist for nonprofits aren't good enough, and I had a clear idea of what a better one would look like.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">I have run large systems, managed teams, and worked at Silicon Valley SaaS companies. I have also done a lot of consulting for nonprofits — migrations, integrations, fixing other people's messes. This product comes out of both sides of that experience.</span></p>",
