                                    "label": "Band 2 — Pull-quote (Boris Cherny, AI Ascent 2026)",
                                    "config": {
                                        "content": "<p><em style=\"background-color: transparent;\">\"Right now you can be a tiny startup; you can build a thing that is as valuable as a large company. And you can actually compete head to head. Because a large company has to evolve their business process — they have to evolve the way they work. They have to retrain everyone to use technology and there's a lot of internal resistance to that. But no one here has that problem.\"</em></p><p class=\"ql-align-right\"><em><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">— Boris Cherny at <a href=\"https://youtu.be/SlGRN8jh2RI?t=747\">AI Ascent 2026</a></span></em></p>",
